"{\"uid\": \"independent.co.uk-sport-olympics-jazmin-sawyers-injury-paris-2024-olympic-games-b2553586.html\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Notifications can be managed in browser preferences.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 52, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Please refresh the page or navigate to another page on the site to be automatically logged inPlease refresh your browser to be logged in  Swipe for next article  Exclusive interview:The British long jumper tellsThe Independentabout her long road to recovery after being ruled out of this summer's Paris Olympics and the importance of a life outside athletics  Removed from bookmarks  I would like to be emailed about offers, events and updates from The Independent.\", \"from\": 54, \"to\": 519, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 240, \"end\": 247, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.9995578371179917, \"rank\": 0.00035149724474037476, \"text\": \"British\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}, {\"begin\": 351, \"end\": 365, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1924_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Paris Olympics\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1924_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1924_Summer_Olympics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Read ourPrivacy notice  Injuries can often be a curious paradox.\", \"from\": 520, \"to\": 584, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Now, reflecting on the ruptured Achilles that has cruelly denied her a chance to compete at this summer'sParis Olympics, Jazmin Sawyers realises that more than most.\", \"from\": 585, \"to\": 750, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 617, \"end\": 625, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Achilles_tendon\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.5626730734578052e-15, \"text\": \"Achilles\", \"types\": [\"Q4936952\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Achilles_tendon\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Achilles_tendon\"}, {\"begin\": 706, \"end\": 720, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jazmin_Sawyers\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Jazmin Sawyers\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jazmin_Sawyers\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jazmin_Sawyers\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"There was nothing abnormal about her start to training camp in Turkey or her warm-up that particular morning in mid-April but, sometimes, the most serious injuries can be born out of the most innocuous of circumstances.\", \"from\": 752, \"to\": 971, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 815, \"end\": 821, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Turkey\", \"score\": 0.9763799205613722, \"rank\": 0.023741665434938032, \"text\": \"Turkey\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Turkey\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Turkey\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And yet, perhaps it is the freakish way in which Sawyers sustained the rupture - merely jumping over a hurdle - that allows her to speak so candidly about the injury just five weeks after undergoing surgery that will likely see her sidelined for 12-14 months.\", \"from\": 973, \"to\": 1232, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The way it happened is one of the things that has helped me deal with the injury,\\\" she tellsThe Independent.\", \"from\": 1234, \"to\": 1343, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It was a normal training day, I was doing what I have done hundreds if not thousands of times before and there were no signs.\", \"from\": 1343, \"to\": 1469, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I was doing nothing unusual, nobody missed anything.\", \"from\": 1470, \"to\": 1522, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"At first I thought I'd clipped the hurdle but my Achilles had just snapped - plain and simple.\", \"from\": 1524, \"to\": 1619, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1574, \"end\": 1582, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Achilles_tendon\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.5626730734578052e-15, \"text\": \"Achilles\", \"types\": [\"Q4936952\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Achilles_tendon\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Achilles_tendon\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Having spoken to other people who have had the same injury, it's one of those that can just come out of nowhere.\", \"from\": 1620, \"to\": 1732, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"But that initial feeling that I would not be going to the Olympics - that the work I'd done in the lead-up to Paris was for nothing - was heartbreaking.\\\"\", \"from\": 1733, \"to\": 1886, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1843, \"end\": 1848, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999986358, \"rank\": 1.5720713818630313e-12, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Sawyers had every right to be heartbroken.\", \"from\": 1888, \"to\": 1930, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Having finished eighth at her first twoOlympic Games- in Rio and Tokyo - the British long jumper enjoyed her breakthrough moment at last summer's European Indoor Championship when sheclaimed gold with a personal-best leap of seven metres.\", \"from\": 1931, \"to\": 2169, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1988, \"end\": 1991, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2016_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9998909826601466, \"rank\": 0.00010902922604339214, \"text\": \"Rio\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2016_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2016_Summer_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 1996, \"end\": 2001, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"score\": 0.8266044469009831, \"rank\": 0.20976628041147985, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\"}, {\"begin\": 2008, \"end\": 2015, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.9995578371179917, \"rank\": 0.00035149724474037476, \"text\": \"British\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}, {\"begin\": 2077, \"end\": 2092, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/European_Athletics_Indoor_Championships\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"European Indoor\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/European_Athletics_Indoor_Championships\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/European_Athletics_Indoor_Championships\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Missing out on her third Olympic appearance in Paris is a tough pill to swallow, but the 30-year-old has maintained a remarkable sense of perspective and is determined to not let the injury dent her ambitions of scaling the sport's summit.\", \"from\": 2171, \"to\": 2410, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2218, \"end\": 2223, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999986358, \"rank\": 1.5720713818630313e-12, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Because it's such a major injury, I think I found it easier to accept,\\\" she insists.\", \"from\": 2412, \"to\": 2497, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Within 24 hours, I was looking ahead going, 'Okay, when can I be back by?'\", \"from\": 2498, \"to\": 2573, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The upset over the Olympics still lingers in the background, but I am much more focused on how can recover and return even better at the World Championships next year.\", \"from\": 2574, \"to\": 2741, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"People do not believe me, a lot of my teammates come up and ask: 'How are you?\", \"from\": 2743, \"to\": 2822, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Are you okay?'\", \"from\": 2823, \"to\": 2837, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"And I am like, 'I am doing great' and it's true.\", \"from\": 2838, \"to\": 2886, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I understand it seems counterintuitive to suggest, I might be doing great, but I am.\", \"from\": 2887, \"to\": 2971, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"This has happened.\", \"from\": 2973, \"to\": 2992, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"There is nothing I can do about it and I feel like that truth settled on me so quickly.\", \"from\": 2993, \"to\": 3080, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I am a positive person but I also know how serious these injuries can be for jumpers.\", \"from\": 3081, \"to\": 3166, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I am so determined to ensure that this setback does not define me and is not a career-ending moment.\\\"\", \"from\": 3167, \"to\": 3268, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Part of what helps Sawyers retain that perspective in the wake of such a crushing injury is that she's never let her jumping define her.\", \"from\": 3270, \"to\": 3406, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Yes, she's an athlete.\", \"from\": 3407, \"to\": 3429, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"But she's also a law graduate, a singer and an amateur dressmaker in her spare time.\", \"from\": 3430, \"to\": 3514, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"While rehab already has back at Loughborough, aided by her former team-mates who drive her to and fro, Sawyers is hoping her extended summer break can afford more time to tap into the things she enjoys outside of her chosen profession.\", \"from\": 3516, \"to\": 3751, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3548, \"end\": 3560, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Loughborough\", \"score\": 0.876712271584168, \"rank\": 0.14062491793721715, \"text\": \"Loughborough\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Loughborough\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Loughborough\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I have always tried to be an athlete that advocates for having a whole full life outside of your sport largely because something like this can happen that can take that away from you,\\\" she explains.\", \"from\": 3753, \"to\": 3952, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I am hoping to make some more outfits, maybe release some music and try to perform a little bit.\", \"from\": 3954, \"to\": 4051, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Just really lean into those sides of me that do not get the attention when athletics is at the forefront because I am all of those things rather than just an athlete.\\\"\", \"from\": 4052, \"to\": 4219, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Her latest venture this summer could be a foray into broadcasting after dipping her toe into it at last year's World Championships.\", \"from\": 4221, \"to\": 4352, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Another long-held dream of hers, Sawyers has already begun discussions about possible media opportunities for the Paris Games and hopes the achievements of her peers can keep her motivated during her lengthy comeback.\", \"from\": 4353, \"to\": 4570, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's a dream separate from the dream of being on the track and winning a medal,\\\" she says.\", \"from\": 4572, \"to\": 4663, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Like I said, I am an athlete first, but [I am] all these other things as well.\", \"from\": 4664, \"to\": 4743, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"One of those dreams is being able to help broadcast an Olympic Games.\", \"from\": 4744, \"to\": 4813, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I think there will be moments where it'll be hard and I will wish that I was down there on the track but it will be my friends that I get to watch.\", \"from\": 4815, \"to\": 4963, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I see how hard these people work, not only for their own dreams but supporting me and everything that I do so it will be nice to show them how much they mean to me.\", \"from\": 4964, \"to\": 5128, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"And I know that I will be back down on that track the following year.\", \"from\": 5130, \"to\": 5200, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"This summer may be a little interlude but I have still got that fire in my belly and watching them compete will only stoke the flames that bit more.\\\"\", \"from\": 5201, \"to\": 5350, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We spoke to Jazmin in her ambassadorial role forAmerican Pistachio Growers.\", \"from\": 5352, \"to\": 5427, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5409, \"end\": 5418, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pistachio\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.747685878122605e-18, \"text\": \"Pistachio\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pistachio\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pistachio\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Pistachios provide complete protein and contain antioxidants like vitamin E, two nutritional qualities which are hugely beneficial to fuelling exercise and aiding injury recovery.\", \"from\": 5428, \"to\": 5607, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Join thought-provoking conversations, follow other Independent readers and see their replies  Please refresh the page or navigate to another page on the site to be automatically logged inPlease refresh your browser to be logged in\", \"from\": 5609, \"to\": 5839, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5660, \"end\": 5671, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Independent\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.497749724021297e-21, \"text\": \"Independent\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q234460\", \"Q11032\", \"Q1092563\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Independent\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Independent\"}]}]}"